#GETTHELOOK💄 GEORGINA RODRIGUEZ’S SUPERMODEL GLAM! ✨

Darlings, want to re-create @sofiatilbury’s viral 90s supermodel glam on the beautiful @georginagio - the star of my NEW! Super Nudes campaign? Here’s everything you need! 😍

✨ HOLLYWOOD CONTOUR WAND 
My easy liquid contour that sculpts and shapes the look of your face! Dot the magic cushion applicator onto the hollows of your cheeks, across your temples + along your jawline. Buff upwards with my NEW! Super Nudes SHAPEWEAR™Brush. 

✨ BEAUTY LIGHT WAND IN SPOTLIGHT
My award-winning highlighter! Apply to your cheekbones, brow bone and Cupid’s Bow using the magic cushion applicator. Blend using my NEW! Super Nudes SHAPEWEAR™Brush.

✨ BROW CHEAT 
My micro-precision refillable eyebrow pencil! Use the brush side to comb hairs upwards. Add in texture + tint with the angled tip to create the illusion of defined, natural brow hairs. 

✨EXAGGER-EYES VOLUME MASCARA
My smudge-proof, flake-proof, sweat-proof, clump-proof + humidity-proof mascara! Press the inner curved side into the root of the lashes and pull upwards. Use the outer curved side and wiggle the bristles from side to side to separate, lift, and define.

✨ NEW! LIP CHEAT CONTOUR DUO IN TAN
Trace along the outer edge of your natural lip line with the ‘SCULPT’ end. Gently diffuse using your finger tip or a lip brush. Overline your Cupid’s Bow to emphasise! Using the ‘FILL’ end, fill your lips from the centre outwards to create a soft blend into the ‘SCULPT’ shade for an enhanced, fuller-looking pout! 

✨BIG LIP PLUMPGASM IN NEW! NUDEGASM DIAMONDS
My viral plumping-effect gloss for lips that look 93% plumper instantly!* In NEW! Nudegasm Diamonds. Apply directly onto your lips with the precision application diamond tip! The applicator adds the perfect amount to your lips every time! 

For more artistry, follow @sofiatilbury! 💄💫

*Tested on 220 people for 1 week.
